title: ELEMENT "WILD CARD" MAKE IT COUNT - 2012 VIDEO CONTEST
description:
If the MAKE IT COUNT Contest Series didn't stop in your town, you still have a chance to compete and make it to the finals. Submit a 1-minute video of you at your local park to win an experience of a lifetime; a trip to the finals at Element YMCA camp and The Berrics.

One overall video contest winner will receive an all expenses paid trip to join fellow winners from around the world at Element YMCA camp, followed by a day at The Berrics with the Element team, and the chance to compete for Element sponsorship.

RULES

Submit a one minute video of you, at one skatepark.
All videos must be submitted by July 1st.
Winner announced July 15th.
